{"tid":2285431,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"泫雅頻頻派福利 真空上陣夾胸晒事業線","createTime":"2020-11-14T05:55:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-14T06:52:57.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"923e2eaf71651288e1bb44eb123cdaad1d9e19d7","tid":2285431,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T05:55:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Vs4y3nSyY6yCrVFxPL6bFbAUFAg=/720x405/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MOVMIWW6URHEPGQF4G42GF65D4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FVs4y3nSyY6yCrVFxPL6bFbAUFAg%3D%2F720x405%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMOVMIWW6URHEPGQF4G42GF65D4.jpg&h=2aa142ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n泫雅又在IG派福利。<br />\n<br />\n現年28歲的韓國「馬舞女」泫雅，早前因血管迷走神經性昏厥復發，所屬事務所P NATION表示以治療為優先，決定延遲推出新碟《Good Girl》，泫雅亦會停工休養至情況好轉才復工。<br />\n<br />\n雖然泫雅未有宣佈正式復工，但她就頻頻更新IG讓fans得知其近況，而一向大方騷身材的她，昨日再度上載性感照誘fans。泫雅穿上白色外套搭配黑色超短裙出鏡，露出纖腰及白滑長腿，由於外套只拉了三份一的拉鏈，明顯可見泫雅似乎真空上陣，擺出多個甫士的她更夾胸晒事業線，獲fans大讚性感惹火，未知男友E&rsquo;Dawn看到會有甚麼反應？"},{"pid":"1bffb3e03f24c42d79448d228a0944717ba1640b","tid":2285431,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T05:56:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Clq06wM_MR1FYziT8s9tVu8b5rs=/802x1002/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BGPBDTVDRFG5BDQPEBCEVTCFLA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FClq06wM_MR1FYziT8s9tVu8b5rs%3D%2F802x1002%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBGPBDTVDRFG5BDQPEBCEVTCFLA.jpg&h=8034b492&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ot1n4lX15OBrRj2l1hjTKqfiY2E=/802x1002/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XDCBHOAW